    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes requirements and solutions for MPLS-TP Shared
   Ring Protection (MSRP) in the ring topology for point-to-point (P2P)
   services.  The mechanism of MSRP is illustrated and analyzed how it
   satisfies the requirements in RFC5654 for optimized ring protection.</t>
